sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant AD as Administrator
  participant SRC as Source Tree
  participant BE as FastAPI Backend (8001)
  participant WK as Background Workers
  participant FE as Next.js Frontend (3000)
  participant SYS as systemd / supervisor
  AD->>SRC: pull release + set .env (secrets masked)
  AD->>BE: run DB migrations (SQLite)
  AD->>SYS: enable backend service
  SYS->>BE: start API + poller + watcher
  BE->>WK: launch workers (heartbeat registered)
  AD->>FE: build + start dashboard
  AD->>SYS: enable frontend service
  AD->>BE: health checks (services, ES, Redis)
  BE-->>AD: healthy
  AD->>AD: harden (firewall, restricted ports, admin secret)
